    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A caption about climate change in Science Times yesterday omitted one picture credit and misstated another. The picture of a protester dressed as a polar bear was taken by Steve Morgan for Greenpeace. The picture of David Barber, a Canadian climatologist, was taken by Diana Wilmar for the Discovery Times Channel, not Phil Marino for The New York Times.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
